      "en": "الصِّرَاطَ الْمُسْتَقِيمَ — 'the straight path.' الصِّرَاطَ is the noun, الْمُسْتَقِيمَ is the adjective that follows it. Both carry ال because they are definite. You ask Allah for this exact phrase seventeen times every day. Now you see the grammar inside your du'a.",
